= Easy TeX
A barebones project for easily getting up and running with
TeX

== Instructions
# Download [[http://www.tug.org/mactex/2011/|MacTeX]] and install it
# {{{git clone git@github.com:blazingcloud/easytex.git}}}
# {{{mv easytex PROJECT_NAME}}}
# Change the git remote to point to a new repository
## Better yet, just copy the Makefile and create a src/ dir in your new project folder
# To build src/*.tex into doc/*.pdf, run {{{make}}}
# To delete doc/*.pdf, run {{{make destroy}}}
